\n<Manu><WordWrap>Hey Belle, I finished serving the customers here in the restaurant.
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Yep. Talked to the waiter at the back and served all the batchoy to the customers.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Finally...Thanks for your help so much, without your help, we would be in so much trouble...

After serving and helping the restaurant serving batchoy to it's customers,
Belle and the staff waited patiently for the customers to leave the shop.
The staff at the back began leaving as soon as the customers left the restaurant.
\n<Manu><WordWrap>It was nothing, glad I was able to help.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Whats your name and why are you doing here?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>My name is Manu and I'm here to compete in the Gastropolis competition. But it looks like I won't be able to cause I came here instead.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>That's a shame, why did you come here instead of the competition?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>I came here because of the scent, I was captivated by the smell that I...
\n<CHEF><WordWrap>WHERE HAVE YOU BEEN?, I HAVE BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU EVERYWHERE!
\n<CHEF><WordWrap>NO TIME TO EXPLAIN MANU, WE HAVE TO GO THE CAPITOL NOW OR WE WILL MISS PAZ LATCHOY!

CHEF and Manu left the restaurant as fast as possible,
and reach the Capitol to see Paz Latchoy.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Maun you came back! So how was the competition?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>I wasn't able to reach on time...
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Anyways, do you know a way for me to reach Paz Latchoy himself? I wan't able to see him because of the dense crowd.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>You want to see Mr. Paz himself?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Please I need your help, this might be my final chance to be able a chef.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Since you helped me with the restaurant, I'll help you out.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>There are many places where Mr. Paz might be but you best bet on finding him ist at the Jaro Market.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>That's where his original restaurant was, but as his popularity grew so did his franchise.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>He's usually there most of the time, thats your best bet of ginding him.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>If your wondering where the Jaro Market is, its jut up ahead. Follow the road straight above and you'll reeach the Jaro Market.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Mention that Belle sent you there and mention him that you helped around his restaurant.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>There's a chance he will return a favor if you mention that you helped around the restaurant.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>But that's a guess, thats all I the info I can give you. I hope it helps you.
\n<Manu><WordWrap>It's enough information, thank you for helping me, I don't know how to repay you.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>You already repayed by helping the restaurant itself. I just returned a favor.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>You better go now before he leaves his restaurant.
Head to the Jaro Market to find Paz Latchoy

\n<Belle><WordWrap>Like I said go to the Jaro Market and go to his original restaurant.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>The Jaro market is up ahead, follow the road that goes up and you'll reach the market.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Hurry now, you might miss himn again. This is your last chance.
Head to the Jaro Market to find Paz Latchoy
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Oh excuse me. Hello there welcome to the Paz Latchoy's Batchoyan.
\n<Manu><WordWrap>What is this fragrant smell? It smell so good...
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Smell? Oh you're referring to the batchoy. That's a house hold recipe that the founder Paz latchoy is famous for.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>It has garnered a reputation for being a good hearty dish for the common folk.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>If you're here for a piece of batchoy, I'm sad to say that we cannot serve any to you as of now...
\n<Belle><WordWrap>You see, we're short on staff and we lack the man power to finish making batchoy currently.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>Not only that but the customer's here have been waiting for a while for their batchoy and have becomming more angry...
\n<Belle><WordWrap>I'm sorry that we cannot serve you any batchoy...
\n<Manu><WordWrap>I can help you out with your problem. I'm somwwhat of a chef my self.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>What choice do I have. Fine you can help, head to the kitchen that's in the back.
\n<Belle><WordWrap>You can't miss it, just turn up and you can reach the kitchen.
Head to the kitchen to help serve the customers their Batchoy
